<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to AI Professor</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .credentials-box {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .password {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-alert {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="AI Professor Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Welcome to AI Professor! üéâ</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        
        <p>Your {{role}} account has been successfully created on our AI Professor platform. Below are your login credentials:</p>
        
        <div class="credentials-box">
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong></p>
            <div class="password">{{password}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="security-alert">
            <p>‚ö†Ô∏è For your security, please change this password immediately after your first login.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <p><strong>Important Security Notice:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Please change your password after your first login</li>
                <li>Do not share your credentials with anyone</li>
                <li>Keep your password secure and confidential</li>
                <li>You can reset your password after login if needed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can now log in to your account and start exploring the AI Professor platform. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact your school administrator.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The AI Professor Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent automatically. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>